    },
    {
      "id": "dots_in",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 378,
      "y": 112,
      "strokeColor": "#888",
      "text": "... (C=128 channels)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.850Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.850Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "step2_label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 180,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "text": "STEP 1: compute denominator for channel i=1",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.850Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.850Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 205,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 110,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.850Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.850Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom_eq1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 215,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Σⱼ γ₁ⱼ · wⱼ²  =  γ₁₁·w₁²  +  γ₁₂·w₂²  +  γ₁₃·w₃²  + ...",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom_eq2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 238,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "          =  0.4·(2.3)²  +  0.1·(-1.8)²  +  0.3·(3.1)²  + ...",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom_eq3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 261,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "          =  0.4·5.29  +  0.1·3.24  +  0.3·9.61  + ...",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom_eq4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 284,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "          ≈  2.116  +  0.324  +  2.883  + ...  ≈  6.8",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom_note",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 302,
      "strokeColor": "#c07000",
      "text": "γ is symmetric (γᵢⱼ = γⱼᵢ), so ALL channels influence channel i's normalization",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "step3_label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 340,
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "text": "STEP 2: add bias β₁ and take sqrt  →  final denominator",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom2_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 362,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 55,
      "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff",
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom2_eq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 375,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "denom₁ = √(β₁ + Σⱼ γ₁ⱼ·wⱼ²)  =  √(1.0 + 6.8)  =  √7.8  ≈  2.79",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "denom2_note",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 398,
      "strokeColor": "#6a1f9a",
      "text": "β₁ > 0 ensures we never divide by zero  (β is learned, constrained ≥ 2⁻⁵)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "step4_label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 440,
      "strokeColor": "#0c8599",
      "text": "STEP 3: divide  →  normalized output",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "out_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 462,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 55,
      "backgroundColor": "#99e9f2",
      "strokeColor": "#0c8599",
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "out_eq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 475,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "u₁ = w₁ / denom₁  =  2.3 / 2.79  ≈  0.82",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "out_note",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 499,
      "strokeColor": "#0c5e6e",
      "text": "output magnitude is bounded — high-energy neighborhoods get more suppressed",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "step5_label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 540,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "STEP 4: repeat for every channel  →  GDN output vector",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
